3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper presents novel algorithms for graph bipartitioning and ordering, which are fundamental problems in data structures and algorithms.

5. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) - The paper deals with graph partitioning and ordering, which are topics in discrete mathematics.
